Description: 
v4l2codecs: Match V4L2_PIX_FMT_NC12 handling with V4L2
 format

Commit b275f63b1318 ("v4l2codecs: format: Add V4L2_PIX_FMT_NC12")
added the handling based on DRM format and modifier.
We're about to add the replacement V4L2_PIX_FMT_NV12MT_COL128 as a
full GStreamer format, match on V4L2 pixel format to avoid forcing
the new format to have the same constraints.

 gst-plugins-bad1.0 (1.26.2-3) unstable; urgency=medium
